    "en": {
      "title": "Three fuel ships are approaching",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Power and Energy Minister Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera says that three fuel ships are scheduled to arrive in Colombo this week.",
        "The minister mentioned that a ship carrying diesel is scheduled to arrive between tomorrow (12th) and 15th, a crude oil ship between 14th and 16th of this month, and a fuel oil ship between 15th and 17th of this month. does",
        "The minister further said that the rest of the money for the petrol ship which is scheduled to arrive between the 17th and 19th of this month should be paid tomorrow (12th)."
      ],
